Package org.hibernate.type.descriptor.jdbc

Interface JdbcTypeIndicators

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseSqmToSqlAstConverter, BasicValue, BasicValueBinder, DependantBasicValue, MultiTableSqmMutationConverter, StandardSqmTranslator, SybaseSqmToSqlAstConverter
    public interface JdbcTypeIndicators
    More-or-less a parameter-object intended for use in determining the SQL/JDBC type recommended by the JDBC spec (explicitly or implicitly) for a given Java type.
    See Also:
    BasicJavaType.getRecommendedJdbcType(org.hibernate.type.descriptor.jdbc.JdbcTypeIndicators)
